<section class="hero">
    <div class="badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i> It’s just 1 Structure — Use Everywhere.</div>
    <h1>Grammar103: <span class="hi">“than most other”</span></h1>
    <p class="sub">Don't just memorize phrases. Master the <b>STRUCTURE</b> and apply it to every module of the IELTS exam.</p>
    
    <div class="jumpRow">
        <button class="jump" onclick="scrollToId('grammar')">Grammar</button>
        <button class="jump" onclick="scrollToId('wt1')">Writing Task 1</button>
        <button class="jump" onclick="scrollToId('speaking')">Speaking (DRW)</button>
        <button class="jump" onclick="scrollToId('wt2')">Writing Task 2</button>
        <button class="jump" onclick="scrollToId('pron')">Pronunciation</button>
    </div>

    <div class="structureCard">
        <div class="mono">Subject + be (am/is/are/was/were) + Comparative Adjective + than most other + Plural Noun</div>
        <div class="serif" style="margin-top:10px;">Example: "This strategy is more effective than most other methods."</div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="grammar">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-diagram-project hi"></i> 1st Portion: Grammar</h2>
    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr><th>No.</th><th>IELTS Context Examples</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td>1</td><td class="serif">This city is <b>more expensive</b> than most other cities in the country.</td></tr>
            <tr><td>2</td><td class="serif">Online education is <b>more flexible</b> than most other learning systems.</td></tr>
            <tr><td>3</td><td class="serif">Renewable energy is <b>cleaner</b> than most other energy sources.</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</section>

