    <div class="qaGrid">
        <div class="qaCard">
            <p><b>Scenario:</b> Bar Chart - Population in Asia vs others.</p>
            <div class="practice">
                <p>The population in Asia <select class="gap" data-ans="was higher">
                    <option value="">Select</option>
                    <option>was high</option>
                    <option>was higher</option>
                    <option>is higher</option>
                </select> than most other <select class="gap" data-ans="regions">
                    <option value="">Select</option>
                    <option>region</option>
                    <option>regions</option>
                    <option>area</option>
                </select> in the chart.</p>
                <div class="ans-hint">Correct: was higher + regions</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="qaCard">
            <p><b>Scenario:</b> Process Diagram - Cooling Phase.</p>
            <div class="practice">
                <p>The cooling stage <select class="gap" data-ans="took longer">
                    <option value="">Select</option>
                    <option>took long</option>
                    <option>takes long</option>
                    <option>took longer</option>
                </select> than most other <select class="gap" data-ans="steps">
                    <option value="">Select</option>
                    <option>step</option>
                    <option>steps</option>
                    <option>part</option>
                </select> in the process.</p>
                <div class="ans-hint">Correct: took longer + steps</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="speaking">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-microphone hi"></i> 3rd Portion: Speaking (DRW Method)</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><b>DRW</b> = <b>D</b>irect Answer + <b>R</b>eason + <b>W</b>hy/Widening (Comparison)</p>
    
    <div class="qaCard" style="border-left: 5px solid var(--primary); margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h3>Topic: Hometown</h3>
        <p><b>Q: Is your hometown a good place for tourists?</b></p>
        <p class="serif">"Yes, absolutely (D). It has a very rich history and beautiful architecture (R). In fact, it is more attractive than most other tourist destinations in my province (W)."</p>
    </div>

    <div class="structureCard">
        <h3>Interactive Practice: DRW Fill-in</h3>
        <div class="practice">
            <p><b>Topic: Technology</b></p>
            <p>Q: Do you think robots are useful?</p>
            <p>Ans: Yes, I do. Robots <select class="gap" data-ans="are more efficient">
                <option value="">Select</option>
                <option>are efficient</option>
                <option>are more efficient</option>
                <option>is efficient</option>
            </select> than most other <select class="gap" data-ans="inventions">
                <option value="">Select</option>
                <option>invention</option>
                <option>inventions</option>
                <option>thing</option>
            </select> because they never get tired.</p>
            <div class="ans-hint">Correct: are more efficient + inventions</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="wt2">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-pen-nib hi"></i> 4th Portion: Writing Task 2</h2>
    <div class="qaCard">
        <p><b>Topic:</b> Should governments invest in public transport or roads?</p>
        <p><b>Sample Sentence:</b> "Investment in railways is <b>more sustainable</b> than most other <b>infrastructure projects</b> because it reduces the carbon footprint."</p>
        
        <div class="practice">
            <p>Public transport is <select class="gap" data-ans="more beneficial">
                <option value="">Select</option>
                <option>more beneficial</option>
                <option>most beneficial</option>
                <option>beneficial</option>
            </select> than most other <select class="gap" data-ans="solutions">
                <option value="">Select</option>
                <option>solution</option>
                <option>solutions</option>
                <option>ways</option>
            </select> to urban traffic congestion.</p>
            <div class="ans-hint">Correct: more beneficial + solutions</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

